## Copilot Prompt (paste this)

Implement the “Minimal Grid” theme as specified in README:
1) In `/css/style.css`, add the provided theme variable overrides and utilities (palette, typography, buttons, grid tile hover, gallery image hover).
2) Do not edit `baseline-style.css`. Keep structure and containers unchanged.
3) Only add `.tile` class to gallery anchors if missing; no content changes.
4) Ensure mobile and desktop look clean; no layout shifts.
5) Run a quick HTML validation (close any open tags) and ensure all images keep `alt` text.
6) When done, list the files changed and summarize the visual changes in a short commit message.

Follow the Acceptance Criteria section before finishing.
